reviews.review_text: Great '90s show... Black-Throated Wind re-breakout I collect ALL LTGTRs... just love that tune. Brent had a head full o' steam... and I dig the fact that this is now completely flac'd up... FLAC is so much more convenient for me, and to tell the truth, I pass on some shows just because they are NOT all flac'd up...
